 * code: header-nav
 * name: 导航栏
 * name_en: Navigation Bar
 * description: 中轴品牌导航，支持分翼菜单、分层移动面板和下载按钮
 * category: header
 * region: header
 * @component_end
 *
 * @fields_start
 * group:logo => Logo设置
 * logo.display => 显示Logo:select:yes|yes,no
 * logo.text => 品牌名称:text:Aviator Afterburn
 * logo.subline => 品牌副标题:text:Afterburn deck
 * logo.url => Logo图片:textarea:|留空使用默认图标
 * logo.width => Logo宽度:responsive:56/56|px
 * logo.height => Logo高度:responsive:56/56|px
 * group:navigation => 导航设置
 * navigation.display => 显示导航:select:yes|yes,no
 * navigation.bg_color => 导航背景基础色:color:rgba(8,17,31,0.94)
 * navigation.bg_color_scrolled => 滚动后导航背景色:color:rgba(8,17,31,0.98)
 * navigation.text_color => 导航文字颜色:color:#edf4ff
 * navigation.link_color => 导航链接颜色:color:#edf4ff
 * navigation.link_hover_color => 导航链接悬停颜色:color:#29d0ff
 * navigation.link_font_size => 导航链接字号:number:14|px
 * navigation.link_font_weight => 导航链接字重:number:700
 * navigation.link_gap => 导航链接间距:number:18|px
 * navigation.padding_x => 导航左右内边距:number:16|px
 * navigation.padding_y => 导航上下内边距:number:13|px
 * navigation.min_height => 导航最小高度:number:78|px
 * navigation.box_shadow => 导航阴影:text:0 22px 44px rgba(8,17,31,0.16)
 * navigation.backdrop_blur => 导航背景模糊:number:18|px
 * navigation.use_custom_links => 使用自定义导航:select:yes|yes,no
 * navigation.items => 导航项:textarea:Home=>/\r\nFlight Modes=>#tables\r\nWhy Us=>#advantages\r\nPlayer Notes=>#reviews\r\nFAQ=>#faq|配置格式：名字=>url，一行一个。URL为空时自动补#
 * group:navigation_labels => 导航菜单显示名称（有对应页面时显示，留空使用页面标题）
 * navigation.label_home_page => 首页菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_about_page => 关于我们菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_blog_list => 博客菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_contact_page => 联系我们菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_terms_of_service => 条款菜单名:text:
 * navigation.label_privacy_policy => 隐私政策菜单名:text:
 * navigation.use_subpages => 兼容旧版-使用子页面生成导航:select:no|yes,no
 * group:download_button => 下载按钮
 * download_button.display => 显示下载按钮:select:yes|yes,no
 * download_button.text => 按钮文字:text:Download Flight App
 * download_button.url => 按钮链接:text:#download
 * download_button.bg_color => 按钮背景色:color:#ff6b2c
 * download_button.bg_hover_color => 按钮悬停背景色:color:#29d0ff
 * download_button.text_color => 按钮文字颜色:color:#08111f
 * download_button.font_size => 按钮字号:number:14|px
 * download_button.font_weight => 按钮字重:number:800
 * download_button.border_radius => 按钮圆角:number:999|px
 * download_button.padding_x => 按钮左右内边距:number:18|px
 * download_button.padding_y => 按钮上下内边距:number:10|px
 * @fields_end
